# --- Flutter / Dart (monorepo) ---
**/.dart_tool/
**/build/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.packages
**/.pub/
**/.pub-cache/

# Dart define files (Supabase/Firebase config) should not be committed
**/.dart-define-*.json

# --- Android ---
**/.gradle/
**/local.properties
**/captures/

# --- iOS / macOS ---
**/Pods/
**/.symlinks/
**/Flutter/ephemeral/
**/DerivedData/
**/.xcuserdata/

# --- IDEs ---
**/.idea/
**/*.iml

# --- Firebase / Apple config (credentials) ---
**/google-services.json
**/GoogleService-Info.plist

# --- Firebase tooling ---
.firebase/

# --- Supabase local tooling ---
supabase/.temp/

# --- Misc ---
.DS_Store
*.log
